title: "Can an Uprooted Tree Be Saved in Florida?"
description: "A practical Florida guide to when an uprooted tree may still be recoverable, when removal is usually the safer choice, and what homeowners should watch for after storms."
pubDate: 2026-04-22
updatedDate: 2026-04-22
author: "Gorkem Can"
