title: "Do Palms Need Trimming Before Hurricane Season?"
description: "A practical Florida guide to whether palms should be trimmed before hurricane season, what should and should not be removed, and how overcutting can create bigger problems."
pubDate: 2026-04-22
updatedDate: 2026-04-22
author: "Gorkem Can"
