title: "Large Tree Removal Near Power Lines: Safety First"
description: "A practical Florida guide to why large tree removal near power lines requires extra caution, what homeowners should watch for, and why guesswork is a bad idea."
pubDate: 2026-04-22
updatedDate: 2026-04-22
author: "Gorkem Can"
