title: "Seasonal Trimming for Florida Citrus Trees"
description: "A practical Florida guide to when citrus trimming makes sense, when it does not, and how homeowners can keep citrus trees healthier without overcutting them."
pubDate: 2026-04-22
updatedDate: 2026-04-22
